reviewText: As Expected, On Time. Happy Kid's!
Purchased as gift.  Kids seemed to enjoy the movie.
This is all on one CD, just flip it over.  That works great in my house!  Brand new, can't beat the price either.

I had never seen these versions of Batman, Batman & Robin before, Not too shabby, Not bad at all for the times. Well you can`t compare this Batman to Christian bale. But for entertainment sake I liked the Acting of Val Kilmer as Batman better than George Clooney. I wonder how much was spent on affects in both films?
This was a great value for my money. It arrived as promised and in great condition. This is a terrific addition to my collection and I recommend it for anyone who is a Batman fan.
